{"tid":1905524,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"想問問泛民搶攻功能組別成功之後下一步想點行？","createTime":"2020-03-01T10:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T16:58:40.000Z","uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"18adeb2a60d711a843078af55a9acaa377952442","tid":1905524,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/73/%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%96%BC%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%BB%B3%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA%E6%A8%99%E8%AA%9E%2C_Jul_2019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F7%2F73%2F%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2596%25BC%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E5%25B1%2595%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%25A8%2599%25E8%25AA%259E%252C_Jul_2019.jpg&h=c5098a5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"205de5d8d5604c6a8bf340834982e3dd42d564cf","tid":1905524,"uid":232370,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:22:03.000Z","msg":"功能組別因選民登記時限已過等問題，沒可能奪得超過一半議席(預計只有約12席)，還未算上中共黑箱作業、種票假票等招數。故此沒可能通過普選法案(需2/3立法會議員贊成)或提議任何私人草案(需地區直選及功能組別各有過半數議員支持)，進攻立法會的實際作用只有守住地區直選過半的否決權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先唔講會唔會成功<br />\n哩廿幾年做過乜大家心照啦"},{"pid":"b547d8650e080520c33524a5bd31716ff6ea0acc","tid":1905524,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af61a24c53a5e268e3608f270c2d9385dc27a505","tid":1905524,"uid":260023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"還有一個月的時間<br />\n便會錯失機會<br />\n又一個(空談)的年代<br />\n白白犧牲了這麼多的手足<br />\n<br />\n還有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個月</span></span>的時間<br />\n便會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">錯失機會</span></span><br />\n又一個<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(空談)</span></span>的年代<br />\n白白犧牲了這麼多的手足<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成功</span></span>是要有目標和過程的不是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一步能登天</span></span>!<br />\n贏功能組別 ---&gt; 贏立法會 ---&gt; <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">贏特首選委 ---&gt; 香港人自己選擇特首</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先有機會走下一步</span></span> (立法會普選和特首普選 )<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可惜</span></span>現在整個社會<br />\n也不能專注目標和行動"}]}